    "faqs": {
      "q1": "How do I register as a student?",
      "a1": "Students can register through the system by creating an account using their student ID. You'll need to provide personal information, contact details, and upload required documents. The registration process is verified by school administration.",
      "q2": "Can parents access their child's academic records?",
      "a2": "Yes, parents can view their child's grades, attendance, and academic progress by logging into their parent account.",
      "q3": "What if I forget my password?",
      "a3": "You can reset your password using the 'Forgot Password' link on the login page. You'll receive a password reset link via email. If you don't receive the email, please contact the school IT support.",
      "q4": "Is the system secure?",
      "a4": "Yes, the system uses industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect all student and staff data.",
      "q5": "How do teachers submit grades?",
      "a5": "Teachers can submit grades through their dashboard by accessing the class management section and entering student scores. The system automatically calculates final grades.",
      "q6": "Where can I find exam schedules?",
      "a6": "Exam schedules are posted in the Announcements section and are also available in the student dashboard."
    },
